    "client_msg_id": "81a8611a-7238-4e01-a2e4-7884fa681e07",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Actually it reminds Gherkin somewhat: <https://docs.cucumber.io/gherkin/reference/>\n\nTo make this kind of constraints really work, it will require code and deployment identifiers to be located in single namespace. This way it would be possible to reason about anything in documentation, describe any type of constraints on application or service behavior,\n\nThat's why I look at IPFS with hope.",
    "user": "UCKRZS3DZ",
    "ts": "1542264193.084500",
